          <p class='first-para'>
            I am sure that the hon. Gentleman has.
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0402P0-04656'>
        <a name='S6CV0402P0_20030402_WH_64'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-david-laws' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0402P0_20030402_WH_64' title='Link to this speech by Mr David Laws' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
